Author: Brecht Devleesschauwer [aut, cre],
  Saveria Willimès [aut],
  Carine Van Malderen [aut],
  Peter Konings [aut],
  Niko Speybroeck [aut]
Maintainer: Brecht Devleesschauwer <brechtdv@gmail.com>
Description: Functions to calculate the relative, generalized, and Erreygers
    corrected concentration index; plot Lorenz curves; and decompose health
    inequalities using (generalized) linear models, survival models, and
    regression and binary trees.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0), rpart
